# `prefect-aws`

## Welcome! `prefect-aws` makes it easy to leverage the capabilities of AWS in your flows, featuring support for ECS, S3, Secrets Manager, and Batch. ### Installation To start using `prefect-aws`: ```bash pip install prefect-aws ``` ### Contributing Thanks for thinking about chipping in! Check out this [step-by-step guide](https://prefecthq.github.io/prefect-aws/#installation) on how to get started.
info.name: prefect-aws
info.summary: Prefect integrations for interacting with Amazon Web Services.
